bilingual.source: I used to go skateboarding ages ago.
bilingual.target: 我很久以前常去滑滑板。

bilingual.source: There were dinosaurs here a long time ago.
Yes, I have, but a long time ago.
bilingual.target: 是的，我去过，但很久以前了。

bilingual.source: Dinosaurs were on Earth a long time ago.
bilingual.target: 恐龙很久以前在地球上。

bilingual.source: How do you know it is from long ago?
bilingual.target: 你怎么知道它是很久以前的？

bilingual.source: A long time ago, people built pyramids.
bilingual.target: 很久以前，人们建造了金字塔。

bilingual.source: A long time ago children wrote on slates.

bilingual.source: I flew to the earth in it a long time ago.
bilingual.target: 我很久以前乘它飞到了地球。

list.abstract: ago（英[əˈɡəʊ]，美[əˈɡoʊ]），英语单词，形容词，释义为以前；更早。常见短语搭配为long time ago（很久以前）。例句：Hundreds of years ago, no dandelions (蒲公英) grew in North America.（数百年前，北美没有蒲公英生长。） 做副词时，其近义词有previously、formerly、back；作形容词时，其近义词有previous、past。before是指从过去某一时间起向前推算的若干时间的以前，通常与过去完成时连用；ago指从现在起往前推算一段时间，始终置于所修饰的词之后，与一般过去时连用。
一般有两种释义： ①常压瓦斯油：简称 AGO。指原油蒸馏所得的沸程范围约为200～400℃的馏分，是一种轻质油。它们都是重要的发动机燃料。较重的部分（如300～400℃部分），常作为催化裂化的原料，用以进一步生产轻质油品。随着石油化工的发展，已较广泛地将常压瓦斯油作为石油化工原料用于烃类裂解制取乙烯。 ②一类银的氧化物。

yingyinNormal.en: Will, high school was a long time ago.
yingyinNormal.zh: 高中是很久以前的事了。

yingyinNormal.en: And about an hour ago, we made an offer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大约一小时以前，我们开出了我们的价码。

yingyinNormal.en: It was a long time ago. It was less than a year ago. I know. But so much has happened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很久以前的事了。不到一年前。我知道，但中间发生很多事。

yingyinNormal.en: But Kip didn't even have to be Kip. We just, we handled that all wrong. It was a long time ago.
yingyinNormal.zh: 阿吉也不该受到这样的待遇，我们以前处理得很糟糕，况且那是很久以前的事情。

yingyinNormal.en: Years and years ago there were these people called the Maccabees.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很多年以前，有一群人，叫做玛加伯人。

yingyinNormal.en: Once upon the time, in olden days, a long time ago... Mummy Pig has been up there for a long time. I can hear snoring.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很久以前，在古代的时候，故事是在很久以前。猪妈妈已经在上面待了很久了。我好像听见打呼声了。

yingyinNormal.en: No, about a month ago, she gave her number to some guy in a bar.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，一个月以前，她还把电话号码 留给一个在酒吧认识的男的。

yingyinNormal.en: See, a long time ago, there was this family. The Papá, he was a musician.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很久很久以前，有这样的一个家庭，爸爸是一个音乐家。

yingyinNormal.en: Long ago, our enemy, the Gorg, invited the Boov to a peace meeting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很久以前，我们的敌军，格尔族，邀请波波族参加一个和平会谈。

yingyinNormal.en: Ah, wow! Look at all these kids. It wasn't that long ago I had kids around the house.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看这些孩子，不久以前我的孩子也满屋子跑呢。

yingyinNormal.en: If you recall, I pointed out the Check Engine light to you several months ago.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还记得么，几个月以前，我告诉过你引擎检修灯在闪。

yingyinNormal.en: This is something I long ago came to Peace with in my role as the beta male. Open.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很久以前，当我陷入爱河的时候我是可以打开的，快开。

yingyinNormal.en: That's quite a long time ago, Daddy pig. It's lucky I've kept myself so fit and strong.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是很久以前的事了猪爸爸。真幸运我仍然那么健康和强壮。

yingyinNormal.en: No, remember I came here when I was a little piggy. But that's a long time ago, Daddy Pig. In the olden days. Thank you Peppa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哈哈，不会的，记得吗，我还是个小猪的时候就来过这里了。但是这是很久以前的事情了，猪爸爸。以前的时候。谢谢你，佩奇。

yingyinNormal.en: Long ago, the consort Yao Niang was the favorite of Emperor Li Yu. She was a dancer, like you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很久以前，窅娘是皇帝李煜最爱的妃子，她跟你一样善舞。

yingyinNormal.en: Beth, we're not who we were. What was inappropriate two months ago is appropriate now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 贝思，我们和以前不一样了，两个月前不合适的，现在就合适了。

yingyinNormal.en: Tonight we'll hear the story of Krispy Bear. A long time ago, this little bear was alive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今晚我们讲脆脆熊的故事，很久很久以前 这只小熊还活着 。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, I know I should have told you this a long time ago but I am not Drake Remore, OK.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道，我很久以前就应该告诉你了，我并不是德瑞克雷莫瑞医生。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. What I mean is thousands of years ago, predators survived through their aggressive hunting instincts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可以，我是说几千年以前食肉动物捕猎的本能一直存在着。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my God. That's wild. Yeah, but it was, like, a million years ago, so it doesn't matter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的天，那也太放肆了。是，不过那是很久以前的事了没什么要紧的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: It was 100 years <highlight>ago</highlight> this week that the bottle earned a patent.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 100年前的这个星期，瓶子获得了专利。

examination_example.sentence: Fifteen years <highlight>ago</highlight>, Burberry was at crisis point as their signature check pattern was widely imitated by cheap, imitation brands.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 15年前，巴宝莉(Burberry)正处于危机时刻，因为他们的签名支票模式被廉价的仿制品牌广泛模仿。

examination_example.sentence: Fifty years <highlight>ago</highlight>, nearly 100 percent of men that age were working.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 50年前，这个年龄段的男性几乎100%都在工作。

word_usage.usage: 一般说来, 用了 ago 不可用完成时态, 如可以说 She saw him a week ago, 不可说 She has seen him a week ago。
"最近过去的第二个晚上" 习惯说 two evenings ago。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 指从现在起往前推算一段时间, 始终置于所修饰的词之后, 与一般过去时连用。
或指从过去某一时间起向前推算的若干时间的以前, 通常与过去完成时连用; 或泛指以前, 并不具体指若干时间以前, 可使用现在完成的或过去时; 还可指从将来某一时间起的若干时间以前。

examination_example.sentence: Is it what you studied years <highlight>ago</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是你几年前学的东西吗？

examination_example.sentence: Five years <highlight>ago</highlight>, I used Tinkertoys as a test at the beginning of a term to find out something about my students.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 五年前，我在学期开始时使用Tinkertoys作为测试，以了解一些有关我的学生的信息。

examination_example.sentence: I was able to buy it a little over a year <highlight>ago</highlight> because I had my relatives give me money for my birthday.

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 很久前；很久以前；长久以前

examination_example.sentence: Long <highlight>ago</highlight> and faraway, there lived an old man and woman.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 很久很久以前，住着一对老人和女人。

examination_example.sentence: The suggestion was taken seriously about 10 years <highlight>ago</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这个建议大约在10年前被认真对待。

examination_example.sentence: About a year <highlight>ago</highlight>, an old man got on the bus and said loudly to the driver, "Good morning!"
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大约一年前，一位老人上车，大声对司机说：“早上好！”

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 指从现在起到过去时间的某一点的一段时间，常与一般过去时连用。
指从过去某一时间起向前推算的若干时间的以前，通常与过去完成时连用。before还可以泛指以前，并不具体指若干时间以前，可用于现在完成时态中。
